				<small>(Windows, Linux, Mac)</small>
			</h3>
            <div>
                <p><strong>Windows 8, 8.1</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Download the universal msi installer from <a id="msi-download-url" href="{{ asset('Codebendercc.msi') }}">here</a>.</li>
                    <li>Install it to your computer.</li>
                    <li>Enjoy!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><strong>Windows XP, Vista, 7, Mac, Linux</strong></p>
